-- Popolare di Milano’s Chiesa May Resign, Corriere Says
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2012-01-28T12:38:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-28/popolare-di-milano-s-chiesa-may-resign-corriere-says.html
Banca Popolare di Milano Scarl (PMI) 
General Manager Enzo Chiesa may resign, Corriere della Sera
 reported , without saying where it got the information.  Chiesa is in talks with Chairman Andrea Bonomi to find a
consensual agreement on his resignation, the Italian daily said.  A spokesman for the bank didn’t respond to a phone call
seeking for a comment outside business hours.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt in Milan at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  